-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

#####################################
##About LifeLink 5th sem project ->##
#####################################
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Life link (LL) is a web-based platform designed to efficiently manage and store vital information about blood
donations and inventory in blood banks. This system helps hospitals quickly arrange for blood when needed by
providing real-time data on available blood types and quantities. LL records comprehensive details about the
blood, including donor information and recipient history, ensuring traceability and accountability throughout the
blood donation process.

In addition to managing blood inventory, LL includes a dedicated section for organizing blood donation
campaigns. This feature allows hospitals to efficiently plan and track donation events, capturing essential details
about donors and their contributions. By centralizing this information, LL facilitates the smooth operation of
blood banks and ensures that hospitals can access safe, tested blood in a timely manner. This system plays a
crucial role in supporting healthcare providers, enhancing the reliability and responsiveness of blood transfusion
services.
